Subject: [PATCH 5.12 187/384] drm/amdkfd: Fix UBSAN shift-out-of-bounds warning
Date:   Mon, 10 May 2021 12:19:36 +0200
Message-Id: <20210510102021.050252981@linuxfoundation.org>
